reviewText: There's no way of sharpening this! And though it is packaged and encased well, it's not a product I would buy again. I will just stick with what works: the brow pencil.
Great standard beauty product that you can't beat! This is one product to order while the new ones fall by the wayside.
The pencil part is so hard I cannot line the rim of my eyes at all and it's also difficult to use it on my eyelids. It's fine for the eyebrow if that's all you want it for.

reviewText: Even though I brought this in Medium Brown, it has such a fine point that I can use it with my (somewhat gray; I'm 68) eyebrows. I don't use eyeliner (I use fancy eyelid gel makeup), but I have used pencil eyeliner in the past and this is one of the best on the market!
